{"tid":1485652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和事佬]唔好割蓆 唔好灰心 討論下今日有咩值得檢討","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:42.000Z","uid":46879,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"917b536f3729ff0d7932b4f4948a07ebca558896","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:50.000Z","msg":"叫人走嘅只係心急怕有狗衝出黎又發生衝突<br />\n話人留底係鬼係因為怕有衝突而破壞左今日嘅和理非 先用激將法<br />\n<br />\n相反留底嘅人都係為左大家嘅安全想留守到尾班車<br />\n大家唔要俾信任前線 <br />\n佢地未必可以短時間睇到手機<br />\n俾人屈係鬼會好灰<br />\n<br />\n所以大家理性檢討今天 唔好再嗌交啦 好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5f88a783ff3f844ba4f336c6bb020433804322","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"相信前線 不割蓆"},{"pid":"b87787039abd0889394b9d2752bebd73ea961be3","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"尊重和理非回合 保持冷靜"},{"pid":"dcfc50b0da87a6df438781e1e3dda41ec7877227","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"用行動證明沒有警察 沒有衝突 示威者不是暴徒"},{"pid":"6a2fe039880f130e389505ee742e1d98efb58a2f","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再係出面po嗌交啦"},{"pid":"88259b0f1741174f9b965706e9401d587c969768","tid":1485652,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:34.000Z","msg":"有力氣留底日後去抵抗政權啦"},{"pid":"6b9933132a027a937313df2f32c2186c68666f6c","tid":1485652,"uid":266683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nO7z36x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnO7z36x.jpg&h=5563f555&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}